data.description: Welcome Home! This lovely home welcomes you even before you walk in the front door. Imagine decorating the beautiful front porch for the upcoming holidays, or stepping inside to be greeted by the cozy gas log fireplace in the oversized living room. Entertaining will be a breeze with the formal dining room, four season room and large kitchen. The back yard will be the hang out place in the summer. It's all here! The fully fenced back yard offers a newer above ground pool with deck as well as a deck outside the back door. Also there is a new 2+ car garage.  This is a must see home!
